text: Nina Frausing Pedersen (born 20 June 1991) is a former Danish footballer who used to play for Swedish club FC Rosengård, Liverpool and Brøndby IF. She also played for the Denmark women's national football team. In 2016, she began playing for the Brisbane Roar FC (W-League). She previously played for 1. FFC Turbine Potsdam of the Frauen-Bundesliga, for Fortuna Hjørring of the Elitedivisionen and for Liverpool of the FA WSL. ==Honours== ===Club=== ;Liverpool L.F.C. *FA WSL Winner (1): 2014 ==References== ==External links== * * * * UC Berkeley player profile * UT Austin player profile Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:University of Texas at Austin alumni Category:California Golden Bears women's soccer players Category:University of California, Berkeley alumni Category:Liverpool F.C.
